      "title": "Rishad also helped Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The All Ceylon Muslim Congress led by Mr. Rishad Badurdeen has also decided to support the presidential candidate, Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma.",
        "Mr. Badurdeen informed this in a press conference held today."
